node.text: Check out the interview I did with my friends at OMEGA to mark Olympic Day. We track my @Olympics journey and break down the moment OMEGA’s timekeeping confirmed my split-second victory. #omegaofficialtimekeeper

node.text:
It wasn’t that long ago that I told you guys about The Skills, a new platform I joined to teach the lessons that I’ve learned throughout my career. My favorite part of The Skills is that this isn't just about swimming, and there are courses available to help you outside the pool, across multiple sports & on topics including overcoming adversity, teamwork, goal setting & more.
 
To celebrate there being 20 instructors on the platform now, The Skills is offering 20% off their popular All-Access membership. Use PHELPS at checkout to save 20% and learn from me and a few of my friends; the code is good through the end of the month

node.text:
Athletes shouldn’t have to compromise on taste, nutrition… or their home gym set-up. That’s why NEW @silk ULTRA is upgrading home gyms with all the perks of the real thing so – no matter what life throws your way – you can keep hustling from home. Silk is giving you a chance to win one of 50 Ultra Upgrades to elevate your at-home fitness space, your workouts, and your nutrition.
Feed your at-home fitness fire by completing either my workout shown here or the @alyraisman sweat session (she’s a pro 💪). Enter to win at SilkULTRAUpgrade.com
 
NO PURCH. NECESSARY. Open to leg res US/DC, 18+ (19+ in AL&NE, 21 in MS). Ends 3/7/21 at 11:59:59 pm CT (mail in entries must be postmarked by 3/8/21 & received by 3/15/21). Total ARV of 50 Grand Prizes ($683.60 each) : $34,180.00. Void where prohibited. For details on how to enter w/o workout/selfie, see Official Rules: SilkULTRAUpgrade.com/Rules. Sponsor: Danone, US LLC, 12002 Airport Way, Broomfield, CO 80021. This Sweepstakes is in no way sponsored, endorsed or administered by Instagram.

node.text:
It’s critical I refuel my body with nutrients 30 minutes after every workout, otherwise I completely crash. Post-workout smoothies with Silk Soymilk are one quick way I do this, so I have energy to chase after the kiddos all day. Here are the delicious ingredients you’ll need to blend up this protein-packed and plant-powered smoothie: ✔1 cup Silk Original Soymilk ✔1/2 cup of berries (I prefer blueberries, strawberries, and raspberries) ✔1 banana ✔1/2 avocado
For more, join Team Protein & fuel like a champion with @alyraisman and me: silk.com/teamprotein/ #SilkPartner #Ad
